Legends OBS Cursor

Legends OBS Cursor is an Avalon Reset project. The original visual direction,
rotating momentum dots, click language, packaging, and installer are Avalon Reset
work with Codex assistance.

This project also uses and adapts OBS Lua cursor-effect techniques from
cursor-skin-fx:

  https://github.com/upgradeQ/cursor-skin-fx

